{"tid":1466414,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"跪求文宣聲音版","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:43:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:55:23.000Z","uid":50203,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0ea5f5b73906da9b5f5af85c5986f098ace37431","tid":1466414,"uid":50203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:43:15.000Z","msg":"家門不幸有個藍絲老母，今日發現老母唔會點睇字睇圖，但係錄音就會聽哂，有藍絲廢老旁述嘅片更加會睇哂。<br />\n<br />\n事源啱啱返到屋企就發現老母聽緊一段好很長嘅錄音，話要禁止遊行集會禁止帶口罩乜乜柒柒，即刻醒起佢以往都係會聽哂佢啲豬朋狗友嘅錄音。<br />\n<br />\n家母都算叫識中文字，學歷唔高。由佢發現電話可以錄音之後就大部份時間都只係錄音同聽錄音，我都收過唔少佢forward嘅錄音。我相信有唔少老一輩都係因為見到好多字所以唔睇，或者有好多字唔識所以唔睇，甚至唔識英文字所以唔睇。<br />\n<br />\n錄音對佢地嚟講係好方便好直接，因此唔難發現藍絲經常都係用錄音轉遞假消息以及發表個人偉論，正中呢班老一輩嘅胃口，唔使睇字、有真實感、方便同埋懶。有見及此，希望我地都有錄音版嘅文宣，抗衡藍絲嘅錄音洗腦，亦都救救小弟，救救其他手足被洗腦嘅長輩。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d99ed6ffddb799d4fe795c48501523f7bdc1968","tid":1466414,"uid":50203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:44:29.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2e20439cd9edc06529f34160e0c5c4754e40c6c","tid":1466414,"uid":50203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:45:25.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45b25f4051247b8592d242fe909afcd8d760b6b2","tid":1466414,"uid":50203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:45:59.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c01